{"tid":1439124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實中共同林奠都講得好白，而家唔係應該全面升級咩？","createTime":"2019-08-10T04:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T09:58:17.000Z","uid":14153,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8c29fa799ad710472cf1e0cebd54dd68a9538837","tid":1439124,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"罷完工，以為有咩回應，點撚知都係三幅被，仲屌鳩示威者冇經濟貢獻，搞到經濟差<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家根本除左繼續做文宣之外，更加要積極行動升級，唔好同港共有咩對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和平嘅有罷交稅、阻礙政府部門運作、罷工、罷買罷消費<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人話唔好硬碰送頭，呢個當然同意，但唔代表我地要企返去comfort zone，有得涼冷氣梗係好架，安全梗係好架，但唔代表唔再走上街頭囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭就要付出有風險，你地諗下六位烈士，幾百個可能坐監嘅義士，佢地肯為香港獻出自己，我地唔可以令佢地白白犧牲架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4dbccfa3503db7f7f39692ee9ccac3b7ff3d610","tid":1439124,"uid":3696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:07:51.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"011ad364b94ae2d74139a93355f2ab42845c648d","tid":1439124,"uid":14153,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:09:28.000Z","msg":"停止內鬥，一齊行動升級"},{"pid":"7db8b5e2079b0f8d1336874c1e46655dc3782780","tid":1439124,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:15:07.000Z","msg":"之前成功係因為各自努卜，互不阻大家行動，而家個個話中計陰謀論吹風唔可以勇武，咁樣係自斷手臂，幫港共減壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6516d8ba7022780cf9d64e81d881e35c00040a11","tid":1439124,"uid":274136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期五，日擺買！減少家庭支出</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"df19b4cf1aaa0c012ddb2ee729878953e5f292c6","tid":1439124,"uid":34927,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"大家唔好放棄啊 呢場運動一輸一冷靜落黎就輸十代嫁啦"},{"pid":"8a6b59c0a1c6cfd5478eef65bf03fce200e33c0f","tid":1439124,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd0a118c1fc6b655dd4cfd1982e18e07d16c1ef","tid":1439124,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:33:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f00d3692029b2a826bde2c9990879a91c20e21c","tid":1439124,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"推，狙擊高官"},{"pid":"a2552c70eda1d16ae23148a7658d75733389dcfe","tid":1439124,"uid":267435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c29fa799ad710472cf1e0cebd54dd68a9538837","tid":1439124,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"罷完工，以為有咩回應，點撚知都係三幅被，仲屌鳩示威者冇經濟貢獻，搞到經濟差<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家根本除左繼續做文宣之外，更加要積極行動升級，唔好同港共有咩對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hk